name: api_key
label: API Key
help_text: Enter your API key. If you do not have one follow this link: https://cloud.google.com/maps-platform/#get-started - Make sure you have billing enabled on your Google account. For more details visit this link: https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/maps-static/get-api-key

name: map_address
label: Venue Address
help_text: To use this field you need to have Geocoding API enabled in your Google Maps API. Check this guide to do that: https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/geocoding/get-api-key

name: map_latitude
label: Latitude
help_text: If you input the latitude and longitude data the Venue Address field will be ignored. To get the numbers, follow this guide: https://support.google.com/maps/answer/18539?co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&hl=en
